.SH NAME
c \- Command Line Assistant Client
.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
The Command Line Assistant powered by RHEL Lightspeed is an optional generative AI assistant available within the RHEL command line interface.
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
